260
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:02,720
Phaya, Tharn and Yai. Go to the wood and find out where the cellar is.

261
00:26:03,320 --> 00:26:06,680
Thongthai and Khem, come with me.
We must find the location of Songyod’s safe house.

262
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:09,400
