263
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:13,000
We must find Narong and stop him.

264
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,480
But Songyod is...

265
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:16,560
We’re not going to stand by and watch anyone commit a crime...

266
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:19,000
eventhough the victim has done something unforgiving.

267
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:21,760
(Wailing)

268
00:26:21,760 --> 00:26:25,680
Our job is to devlier them into the hands of the laws.

269
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:27,600
Got it?

270
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:28,680
