284
00:27:29,560 --> 00:27:33,400
(Thrill Sound)

285
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:35,400
Hello, everyone.

286
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:39,880
What you are about to see...

287
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,920
requires parental guidance.

288
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:47,400
Those who wish to walk down this path,

289
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,560
this will be your punishment.

290
00:27:52,320 --> 00:27:54,160
The adults should be more aware...

291
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:59,400
and pay attention to normal people who have no power.

292
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:01,440
People who have been bullied...

293
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:03,480
and the innocent ones who have fallen victims...

294
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:10,080
to an evil and disgusting act like what this rascal did.

295
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:14,200
What he deserves the most...

296
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:22,680
is the punsihment from hell that you are about to witness.

297
00:28:32,560 --> 00:28:35,480
(Screaming)

298
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:36,720
I promise you...

299
00:28:39,120 --> 00:28:41,040
