315
00:29:57,160 --> 00:30:00,840
It’s the justice that I can choose for myself.

316
00:30:02,040 --> 00:30:03,280
And it’s about to be over.

317
00:30:03,600 --> 00:30:05,160
Stop it right now.

318
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:09,640
Your sister probably didn’t want to see her big brother
become a criminal like the man who had hurt her.

319
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:14,280
I’m willing to sacrifice myself for those who once fell victims follow suit.

320
00:30:14,840 --> 00:30:17,240
See you in the LIVE, Inspector.

321
00:30:19,360 --> 00:30:21,480
H...help!

322
00:30:21,840 --> 00:30:23,080
Wait! Hey!

323
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:24,800
Damn it!

324
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:27,280
(Crying in pain)

325
00:30:27,560 --> 00:30:28,480
Fuck!

326
00:30:28,520 --> 00:30:31,720
Inform Phaya and his team that the cellar is in that area.

327
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:33,640
They must hurry up and find the cellar. We’re running out of time.

328
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:34,680
-  Go.   /   - Yes, sir.

329
00:30:46,760 --> 00:30:47,680
Ouch!

330
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:49,760
(Wailing)

331
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:54,160
What’s wrong?

332
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:56,240
He’s going to kill Songyod.

333
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:59,600
(Wailing)

334
00:31:24,040 --> 00:31:24,880
Don’t worry.

335
00:31:26,280 --> 00:31:27,720
I won’t let you die that easily.

336
00:31:28,760 --> 00:31:33,360
Do you think you’re the only one who can escape the hands of laws?

337
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:36,880
I can do that too.

338
00:31:41,360 --> 00:31:42,480
And this is…

339
00:31:46,040 --> 00:31:47,160
Geez, why is it stuck now?

340
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:58,720
(Screaming)

341
00:32:00,760 --> 00:32:02,760
Arghhhh!

342
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:13,760
Stop!

343
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:15,680
It’s over.

344
00:32:17,520 --> 00:32:19,800
You can’t bring her back from death by doing this.

345
00:32:20,120 --> 00:32:23,760
If you kill him, he won’t get to be punished any further.

346
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:28,800
But then no more people will have to fall victims to someone like him.

347
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:33,320
Rin should be happy to see him die slowly and painfully.

348
00:32:33,760 --> 00:32:37,080
But you and your people are ruining my plan.

349
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:42,280
I know you’re disappointed that a scroundel like him hasn’t
served the punishment for what he did.

350
00:32:42,360 --> 00:32:44,480
But that doesn’t mean you should become like him.

351
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:47,120
Let the laws handle these people.

352
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:48,400
The laws?

353
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:52,440
They are only for those who don’t have much enough power or money.

354
00:32:52,760 --> 00:32:53,880
You know that too.

355
00:32:54,520 --> 00:32:57,520
How many cases were sealed off and ended up in silence.

356
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:59,720
Like my sister’s.

357
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:05,680
And look what happened to these scumbags?
They can still start a new and live a happy life.

358
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:07,360
What about my sister?

359
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:10,880
She was having a bright future ahead.

360
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:14,840
She was getting married with the man she loved.

361
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:17,000
But then she was forced to take her own life...

362
00:33:18,520 --> 00:33:20,160
because of what a scumbag like him did to her.

363
00:33:21,600 --> 00:33:24,440
If you want him to serve his punishment...

364
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:26,240
you should keep him alive.

365
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:30,080
If you kill him, he’d no longer be a criminal but a victim.

366
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:32,720
And you would become the criminal instead.

367
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:33,720
I don’t care.

368
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:39,720
I’m going to make him pay for what he did to my sister.

369
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:42,680
